	deploy.DeployCmd.AddCommand(agentEngineCmd)
```

CLI evidence:

```text
$ go run ./cmd/adkgo deploy --help
Available Commands:
  cloudrun    Deploys the application to cloudrun.

$ go run ./cmd/adkgo deploy agentengine --help
Available Commands:
  cloudrun    Deploys the application to cloudrun.
